Package: OptiDesign
Type: Package
Title: Experimental Field Design Utilities for Optimized Layout Construction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
      given   = "Félicien",
      family  = "Akohoue",
      email   = "akohoue.f@gmail.com",
      role    = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2160-0182")
    )
Description: Tools for constructing optimized experimental field layouts,
    including augmented, RCBD-type repeated-check designs, p-rep designs,
    and fixed-grid alpha row-column designs with repeated checks, optional
    grouping from family or relationship matrices, optional post-layout
    dispersion, and optional mixed-model efficiency diagnostics.
